text: Kåfjord ( ; ) is a municipality in Troms county, Norway. The city is the 116th largest by area out of the 356 municipalities in Norway. Kåfjord is the 277th most populous municipality in Norway with a population of 2,071. ==Related pages== *List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 ==References== Category:Municipalities of Troms
